title: The Magician
description: The Magician stands confidently with one hand pointed towards the sky and the other pointed to the ground, symbolizing the heavens and the earth. Here the Magician has the ability to go between the two worlds. The four elements, being earth, water, air, and fire, are placed on the table in front of him. The Magician is harnessing the elements to create, with the symbol of infinity indicating the endless possibilities open to us.
